{"tid":1946743,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Folding@Home 其實有冇用？","createTime":"2020-03-27T20:50:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T05:42:57.000Z","uid":197783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"6543971a46236b55e7eb04504e8c679fa0dad898","tid":1946743,"uid":197783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T20:50:55.000Z","msg":"對研究支那肺炎有冇幫助？<br />\n<br />\n如果有既，不如整隊team 大家爭取上榜， 順便當國際戰線.<br />\n<br />\n申請個隊名<a href=\"https://apps.foldingathome.org/team\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.foldingathome.org%2Fteam&d=4vI%2Bds9fBAKyPIgWEbj3fs5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=ca04a1f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.foldingathome.org/team</a><br />\n集合全世界算力對抗共匪。<br />\n<br />\n最好整個激到支那札札跳既team 名，等支那人加入folding戰線，借佢地d 力去研究自己製造出黎既病毒。"},{"pid":"2ead98da57ec846a750ce62f5ab3f9670ec65a27","tid":1946743,"uid":128117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T21:01:29.000Z","msg":"印象中舊登好似有team玩過<br />\n連登就唔知鳥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be2954717e4b2d6cff6dc830d933f64399caf8bd","tid":1946743,"uid":128117,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T21:03:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">隔離epc果邊就一路都有人folding緊<br />\n最近有返post叫人一齊著顯示卡黎fold<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"0443b8a349db715b4b9b85f2748b21bfff3903d5","tid":1946743,"uid":131430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T01:02:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dcda896d15afb9786bc4cf82d55202a56f5ed9c","tid":1946743,"uid":195827,"like":0,"dislike":1,"sc